{"_id":"kP3mXvRj8nTwQz50","name":"Animate Construct","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Enchanting","tn":10,"range":"2y","duration":"1 hour","description":"AP: 2 | TN: 10t | Resist: None | Skill: Enchanting. Target inanimate construct comes to life as a subordinate character under the caster's control for 1 hour. If the construct has no Rank Value, it becomes Minion (5). When the Spell ends, the construct becomes inanimate again but may be reanimated later. A charged Soulstone placed inside a construct (outside of this Spell) animates it for a number of weeks equal to the Soulstone's Lade.","immutos":"Increased Duration, Construct Genus, Alter Range"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bH7nYsWd4cUgLk61","name":"Animate Limb","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Enchanting","tn":8,"range":"2y","duration":"1 week","description":"AP: 2 | TN: 8t | Resist: None | Skill: Enchanting. Target artificial limb animates under the control of the attached character for 1 week. The character controls it as if it were her natural limb. The limb must be crafted to function generally as a normal limb but need not look like one. Alternatively, this Spell cancels the Useless Limb Condition on an artificial limb. If used to animate a non-mechanical (organic) limb, use the Necromancy Skill instead and change the TN to 10C.","immutos":"Increased Duration, Alter Range"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"tF9qMpEv6xBrNa72","name":"Elemental Weapon","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Enchanting","tn":8,"range":"2y","duration":"1 minute","description":"AP: 1 | TN: 8t | Resist: None | Skill: Enchanting. Requirements: Must include at least one Elemental Immuto. Target weapon (or character's body) gains the effects of the included Elemental Immuto for 1 minute. Any character damaged by the weapon suffers the Elemental Immuto's effects. If cast on a character, her Grappling, Martial Arts, and Pugilism attacks gain the Elemental Immuto. Casting this Spell on the same target again overwrites the first instance.","immutos":"Must include at least one Elemental Immuto; Increased Duration, Alter Range"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"mJ2wDhSk8yVcZn43","name":"Heal","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Enchanting","tn":8,"range":"6y","duration":"Instant","description":"AP: 1 | TN: 8t | Resist: None | Skill: Enchanting. A Living target heals 1/2/3 damage. Each additional time the same character is targeted by this Spell within the same hour (success or failure), the TN increases by +3 or +R (caster's choice each time).","immutos":"Increased Damage, Alter Range, Pulse, Location Genus, Living Genus"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"rN5xBvPu3fHoQe84","name":"Mend Critical","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Enchanting","tn":12,"range":"2y","duration":"Instant","description":"AP: 2 | TN: 12t | Resist: None | Skill: Enchanting. Remove the Bleeding Out Condition or a lasting Critical Effect from a Living target. A lasting Critical Effect can only be removed if it was received within the past 1 minute (extendable with the Increased Duration Immuto). If the Critical Effect destroyed or amputated a limb, this Spell causes it to regenerate — provided there is room and it has not been replaced with a pneumatic limb. This Spell will not revive characters killed by a Critical Effect.","immutos":"Increased Duration, Alter Range"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"cL8mKrGj7tYwDa95","name":"Mental Enhancement","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Enchanting","tn":10,"range":"6y","duration":"1 minute","description":"AP: 1 | TN: 10t | Resist: None | Skill: Enchanting. The target gains the Condition 'Mentally Enhanced +1: This character adds +1 to her Mental Aspects, to a maximum of 5' for 1 minute. Each additional time the same character is targeted within the same hour (success or failure), the TN increases by +3 or +R (caster's choice each time).","immutos":"Increased Duration, Alter Range, Pulse, Location Genus"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"zQ4nFsBt9kXcVm16","name":"Physical Enhancement","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Enchanting","tn":10,"range":"6y","duration":"1 minute","description":"AP: 1 | TN: 10t | Resist: None | Skill: Enchanting. The target gains the Condition 'Physically Enhanced +1: This character adds +1 to her Physical Aspects, to a maximum of 5' for 1 minute. Each additional time a character is targeted within the same hour (success or failure), the TN increases by +3 or +R (caster's choice each time).","immutos":"Increased Duration, Alter Range, Pulse, Location Genus"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"vW6pLhAe2jNuYs37","name":"Shapeshift","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Enchanting","tn":10,"range":"Self","duration":"1 minute","description":"AP: 2 | TN: Variable (10R + Beast's highest Physical Aspect minus caster's lowest Physical Aspect) | Resist: None | Skill: Enchanting. The caster transforms her body (and carried clothing and equipment) into a chosen Beast for 1 minute. She gains the Beast characteristic, all of the Beast's Talents and attacks, and replaces her Physical Aspects with the Beast's (which may affect Derived Aspects). While shifted she may not speak, use manufactured equipment, or cast Spells. The caster may end the Spell prematurely as a (1) Action. Example: Caster Speed -2, Beast Might 4 gives TN = 10R + 6 = 16R. The base TN of 10 listed here is the minimum before the Beast modifier is applied.","immutos":"Increased Duration"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"yT1rCdMo5qKbZx48","name":"Beckon","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Necromancy","tn":10,"range":"12y","duration":"Instant","description":"AP: 1 | TN: 10C | Resist: Willpower | Skill: Necromancy. The target moves a number of yards equal to its Walk Aspect directly toward the caster, ending as close as possible. On a Margin of Success, the caster may instead move the target a number of yards equal to its Charge Aspect.","immutos":"Alter Range, Alternate Resistance, Location Genus, Pulse"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"uR3sJfNk7mPvWe59","name":"Bury","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Necromancy","tn":14,"range":"6y","duration":"1 round","description":"AP: 2 | TN: 14C | Resist: Willpower | Skill: Necromancy. The target is removed from reality for 1 round. When the Spell ends, it reappears in a safe location within line of sight and 1 yard of the caster, unaware that any time passed.","immutos":"Increased Duration, Alter Range, Alternate Resistance"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pX7tLqBm4nVhYa60","name":"Cadaver Mask","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Necromancy","tn":12,"range":"Touch","duration":"Until next sunrise or sunset","description":"AP: 2 | TN: 12C | Resist: None | Skill: Necromancy. The caster removes the face from a target corpse and gains its appearance and voice until the next sunrise or sunset, at which point the face returns to the corpse. Only physical appearance changes (not clothing, height, or weight). The caster gains ++ on all Deceive Challenges to impersonate the person whose face she wears.","immutos":"Increased Duration, Inanimate Genus"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"oK9vDrEg2cSuZi71","name":"Interrogate","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Necromancy","tn":10,"range":"6y","duration":"Instant","description":"AP: 1 | TN: 10C | Resist: Willpower | Skill: Necromancy. A Living target must truthfully answer one question (asked as part of casting) to the best of its ability. The target is aware it has been magically compelled. For each Margin of Success, the caster may ask one additional question. Each additional time the same character is targeted within the same hour (success or failure), the TN increases by +3 or +C (caster's choice each time).","immutos":"Location Genus, Alter Range, Alternate Resistance, Increase Resistance"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"wM5yHfCb8pQnXo82","name":"Mind Control","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Necromancy","tn":14,"range":"6y","duration":"Instant","description":"AP: 2 | TN: 14C | Resist: Willpower | Skill: Necromancy. The caster forces the target (not herself) to take a 1 AP Action of her choice. The Action cannot force the target to attack itself or divulge information, but can cause actions against its nature or dangerously foolish actions.","immutos":"Alter Range, Alternate Resistance, Reduce AP"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"eG4zNmJd6kTwBv93","name":"Raise Undead","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Necromancy","tn":14,"range":"6y","duration":"10 minutes","description":"AP: 3 | TN: 14C | Resist: None (Willpower when controlling existing Undead) | Skill: Necromancy. Target corpse becomes an undead subordinate under the caster's control for 10 minutes with the following alterations: Tenacity increased to 3; all other Mental Aspects lowered to -5; loses Living characteristic and gains Undead characteristic; loses all Mental Aspect-linked Skills; Physical Aspect-linked Skills are halved (round up); Rank Value becomes Peon (4); raised with half Wounds remaining. If it acts on the round it was summoned, it gains the Slow Condition. At the Spell's end, the undead becomes uncontrolled (usually violent). Alternatively, may take control of an uncontrolled Undead of Minion Rank or lower, which may resist with Willpower.","immutos":"Increased Duration, Inanimate Genus, Undead Genus, Alter Range"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"hB8cPxRs3fYoUk04","name":"Subsume Corpse","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Necromancy","tn":10,"range":"6y","duration":"Instant","description":"AP: 2 | TN: 10C | Resist: Df | Skill: Necromancy. Target inanimate corpse crumbles to dust (unsuitable for future reanimation). The caster heals 1/2/3 damage, plus additional damage equal to the corpse's Resilience Aspect (if positive). Alternatively, if cast on a non-corpse Undead target: the target suffers 1/2/3 damage and the caster heals damage equal to the damage inflicted (after damage reduction).","immutos":"Inanimate Genus, Undead Genus, Alter Range, Increased Damage"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"dA2mQwZt7jNvEg15","name":"Terrifying Aura","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Necromancy","tn":12,"range":"Touch","duration":"1 minute","description":"AP: 2 | TN: 12C | Resist: None | Skill: Necromancy. The target gains a terrifying aura for 1 minute. Any Living character that ends a Walk Action within the target's engagement range, or targets the target with an Action, must attempt a TN 10 Horror Duel.","immutos":"Increased Duration, Alter Range, Increase Resistance"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lS6kVbDr4nMuXp26","name":"Conjuring","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Prestidigitation","tn":8,"range":"Intellect Aspect in miles (min 1 mile)","duration":"Instant","description":"AP: 1 | TN: 8M | Resist: None | Skill: Prestidigitation. The caster teleports a previously prepared target object to her hands. Any object the caster could carry may be prepared as a (1) Action by touching it and concentrating. Maximum prepared objects equals the caster's Intellect Aspect (minimum 1). Exceeding this limit requires unpreparing one object first. Range equals the caster's Intellect Aspect in miles (minimum 1 mile).","immutos":"Alter Range"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"iU9hTnGc5xWqYe37","name":"Divination","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Prestidigitation","tn":12,"range":"10 miles","duration":"1 hour","description":"AP: 3 | TN: 12M | Resist: None | Skill: Prestidigitation. The caster enters a trance for 1 hour, her body going limp. She can see and hear as if present at the target location (senses are not augmented — darkness is still dark). She may end the Spell prematurely as a (1) Action. While in the trance, she may take no other Actions and automatically flips a Black Joker on any Defense duels.","immutos":"Increased Duration, Alter Range"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"jC3pMxFk8sZdBn48","name":"Invisibility","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Prestidigitation","tn":10,"range":"Touch","duration":"1 round","description":"AP: 1 | TN: 10M | Resist: None | Skill: Prestidigitation. The target becomes invisible for 1 round. Anyone targeting her is considered to have the Blind Condition for that action; visual detection fails completely. The target still makes sound, displaces air, and leaves footprints — non-visual detection is possible with -- (negative twist) to Notice duels.","immutos":"Increased Duration, Alter Range"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"nE7rYqAm2tVhDs59","name":"Parlor Tricks","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Prestidigitation","tn":6,"range":"6y","duration":"Varies","description":"AP: 1 | TN: 6M | Resist: None | Skill: Prestidigitation. The caster produces one minor effect of her choice from the following list: instantly clean and repair a target's clothes; create a short simple sound (soft bells, a single word) audible to everyone in range; whisper a short sentence audible only to one target in range; move a lightweight object 1 yard; change the flavor of a food or drink for 10 minutes; light a candle, lantern, or similar light source; create a translucent still image within range; create a small orb of magical light (lantern-bright) hovering above the caster's head; open an unlocked door, window, or container; play soft music of the caster's choice for 10 minutes.","immutos":"Alter Range, Increased Duration"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"qH4kBwPs6nGcZo60","name":"Phantasm","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Prestidigitation","tn":12,"range":"10y","duration":"1 minute","description":"AP: 2 | TN: 12M | Resist: None | Skill: Prestidigitation. The caster creates an animated illusion that appears real for 1 minute. All details (what it does, how it can be sensed) must be declared at casting. The illusion does not react to external stimuli unless controlled. It can be seen, heard, and smelled — not touched or tasted. It has no substance; characters passing through it are unharmed. It automatically fools observers with no reason to disbelieve. If a character has reason to disbelieve, she may attempt a TN 10 Centering Challenge; on failure she believes it is real. Physical contact results in automatic disbelief. The caster may take control of the illusion as a (1) Action, altering its form or responses until the start of her next turn. The caster may end this Spell at any time without an Action.","immutos":"Increased Duration, Alter Range, Increase Resistance"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"sF8mNvJd3pXtLr71","name":"Swirling Illusions","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Prestidigitation","tn":10,"range":"6y","duration":"1 round","description":"AP: 1 | TN: 10M | Resist: None | Skill: Prestidigitation. The caster surrounds the target in illusionary duplicates for 1 round. The caster names a suit; any successful attack against the target that does not include the named suit in its final duel total is considered a miss. On her turn, the caster may spend a (1) Action to change the named suit.","immutos":"Increased Duration, Alter Range"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"xB2nCkGt9vQwMo82","name":"Teleport","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Prestidigitation","tn":12,"range":"10y","duration":"Instant","description":"AP: 2 | TN: 12M | Resist: Df | Skill: Prestidigitation. A target within range is teleported to a safe location within range. May also target an unattended object (no resistance needed; caster just meets TN). If an object is held by another character, that character may resist. Cannot teleport objects directly into another character's possession — the object appears at the target's feet instead.","immutos":"Alter Range, Alternate Resistance, Increased Duration"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"aD6pZsHr4mYcWe93","name":"Elemental Engulf","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Sorcery","tn":12,"range":"6y","duration":"Instant","description":"AP: 2 | TN: 12C | Resist: Df | Skill: Sorcery. Requirements: Must include at least one Elemental Immuto. The target suffers 1/2/3 damage. All Sorcery Magia require at least one Elemental Immuto.","immutos":"Must include at least one Elemental Immuto; Increased Damage, Blast, Alter Range, Pulse, Increase Pulse, Undead Genus, Living Genus, Construct Genus, Ignore Character"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fL3wMnTv7qBxKo04","name":"Elemental Nova","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Sorcery","tn":10,"range":"p2","duration":"Instant","description":"AP: 2 | TN: 10C | Resist: None | Skill: Sorcery. Requirements: Must include at least one Elemental Immuto. Every character within p2 (pulse 2 yards) of the caster must pass a TN 10 Evade Challenge or suffer 2 damage. The Challenge TN increases by +2 per Margin of Success achieved by the caster. All Sorcery Magia require at least one Elemental Immuto.","immutos":"Must include at least one Elemental Immuto; Increase Pulse, Increased Damage, Ignore Character"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"gK9rNdEs2jPvYa15","name":"Elemental Projectile","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Sorcery","tn":10,"range":"12y","duration":"Instant","description":"AP: 1 | TN: 10C | Resist: Df | Skill: Sorcery. Requirements: Must include at least one Elemental Immuto. The target suffers 1/2/3 damage. All Sorcery Magia require at least one Elemental Immuto.","immutos":"Must include at least one Elemental Immuto; Increased Damage, Blast, Alter Range"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"hQ5mBcXu6nFwZs26","name":"Elemental Strike","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Sorcery","tn":10,"range":"Engagement","duration":"Instant","description":"AP: 1 | TN: 10C | Resist: Df | Skill: Sorcery. Requirements: Must include at least one Elemental Immuto. The target suffers 1/2/3 damage. Range is melee engagement range. All Sorcery Magia require at least one Elemental Immuto.","immutos":"Must include at least one Elemental Immuto; Increased Damage, Blast"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"iV8pYnGd3kMtRe37","name":"Sleep","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Sorcery","tn":12,"range":"6y","duration":"Instant","description":"AP: 2 | TN: 12C | Resist: Willpower | Skill: Sorcery. A Living target must make a TN 10 Unconsciousness Challenge. The Challenge TN increases by +2 per Margin of Success achieved by the caster.","immutos":"Alter Range, Increase Resistance, Living Genus, Location Genus, Alternate Resistance"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"jT4sKxBr9fNcZq48","name":"Summon Gamin","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Sorcery","tn":12,"range":"6y","duration":"3 rounds","description":"AP: 2 | TN: 12C | Resist: None | Skill: Sorcery. Requirements: Must include at least one Elemental Immuto. A Gamin is summoned within range on a surface that can support its weight, under the caster's control. The caster may command it with the (1) Order Action. If the Gamin acts on the round it was summoned, it gains the Slow Condition. The summoned Gamin disappears after 3 rounds. The Elemental Immuto determines the type of Gamin summoned. All Sorcery Magia require at least one Elemental Immuto.","immutos":"Must include at least one Elemental Immuto; Increased Duration"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"kR7mLvEw2pHdXo59","name":"Telekinetic Movement","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Sorcery","tn":10,"range":"10y","duration":"1 minute","description":"AP: 2 | TN: 10M | Resist: Df | Skill: Sorcery. The caster moves a target object weighing no more than (Intellect x 50) lbs. (minimum 50 lbs.) up to 5 yards in any direction. For the next minute, the caster may spend 1 AP to move the object again without recasting. If the object is a weapon, the caster may make attacks with it (and may Charge with y-range weapons), using the appropriate Skill but replacing the relevant Aspect with Intellect. If the target is unattended, it does not resist. If the target is held by another character, that character may resist.","immutos":"Alter Range, Increased Duration, Alternate Resistance"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lP3nJwDs6qFcYa60","name":"Telekinetic Push","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Sorcery","tn":10,"range":"10y","duration":"Instant","description":"AP: 1 | TN: 10M | Resist: Df | Skill: Sorcery. The target is pushed 1 yard in any direction, plus additional yards equal to the caster's Tenacity Aspect (if positive).","immutos":"Alter Range, Alternate Resistance"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"mN9sQtBr4kZvGe71","name":"Wrench","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-purple.webp","system":{"theory":"Sorcery","tn":12,"range":"6y","duration":"Instant","description":"AP: 2 | TN: 12C | Resist: Toughness (Resilience) | Skill: Sorcery. A Living target must make a TN 10 Toughness Challenge. On failure, it suffers a Moderate Critical Effect. The Challenge TN increases by +2 per Margin of Success achieved by the caster.","immutos":"Increase Resistance, Alter Range, Living Genus, Undead Genus"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
